{{Character | Name=Hod | Guid=3005-27541 | Deck=Lumberjack in Riverwood | Gender=Male | Concepts=Concepts/Lumberjack | Enemies= | Franchises= | Friends=Characters/Frodnar,Characters/Stump | Games=Games/The_Elder_Scrolls_V_Skyrim | Locations=Locations/Riverwood,Locations/Skyrim,Locations/Tamriel,Locations/Whiterun_Hold | People= | Objects=Objects/Axe,Objects/Dagger,Objects/Gold,Objects/Key | Image=https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_super/10/107275/2525093-7296720245-SR-np.jpg }}
<div id='imageData' data-json='{"infobox":{"file":"2525093-7296720245-SR-np.jpg","path":"10\/107275\/","mime":"image\/jpeg","sizes":"square_tiny,square_medium,scale_small,square_small,square_mini,square_avatar,scale_medium,screen_medium,scale_large,scale_avatar,scale_super,screen_kubrick","caption":""},"background":[]}' /> Hod is a Nord lumberjack who lives [[Locations/Riverwood|Riverwood]]. He owns a small mill with his wife, [[Characters/Gerdur|Gerdur]]. They have a son named [[Characters/Frodnar|Frodnar]]. He is flirty, saying to the player that ''"You met Camilla yet? Wouldn't mind getting my hands on those trunks. He he he he." ''and if the player is female, he will add'' ''"Now you, lass... You've got some beautiful trunks yourself... Hmm?"''''
He will buy firewood for 5 gold per piece, and sell the player lumber if Hearthfire is installed. If his disposition is raised high enough, he will also allow you to cut your own lumber for free. He wears a set of miner's clothes and a pair of boots. He carries an iron dagger, an iron war axe, the key to his house, some common loot and gold.

{{Character | Name=K' | Guid=3005-220 | Deck=An anti-hero and the main protagonist of the "NESTS Arc" in the King of Fighters series, K' (pronounced "kay-dash") was abducted by the secret organization NESTS and infused with Kyo Kusanagi's DNA. Unable to control the flames on his own, he uses a special glove to regulate his power. | Gender=Male | Concepts=Concepts/Anti_Hero,Concepts/Byronic_Hero,Concepts/Combo,Concepts/Fire,Concepts/Fire_Manipulation,Concepts/Hand_to_Hand_Combat,Concepts/Male_Protagonists,Concepts/NESTS_Cartel,Concepts/New_Protagonist_in_Sequel,Concepts/Profanity,Concepts/Sexualized_Men,Concepts/Shoto_clone,Concepts/Special_Attack,Concepts/Super_Meter,Concepts/Voice_Acting | Enemies=Characters/Angel,Characters/Igniz,Characters/Iori_Yagami,Characters/K9999,Characters/Krizalid,Characters/Kusanagi_21992,Characters/Kyo_1,Characters/Kyo_2,Characters/Kyo_Kusanagi,Characters/Nameless | Franchises=Franchises/SNK_vs_Capcom,Franchises/The_King_of_Fighters | Friends=Characters/Benimaru_Nikaido,Characters/Foxy,Characters/Kula_Diamond,Characters/Maxima,Characters/Ramon,Characters/Shingo_Yabuki,Characters/Vanessa_3497,Characters/Whip | Games=Games/ACA_NeoGeo_Selection_Vol_4,Games/Days_of_Memories,Games/Days_of_Memories_2,Games/Days_of_Memories_3,Games/Kimi_wa_Hero_Taiketsu,Games/KOF_X_Garou_Densetsu,Games/NeoGeo_Arcade_1,Games/NeoGeo_Battle_Coliseum,Games/Picross_S_SNK_Classics_And_NeoGeo_Edition,Games/SNK_Allstar,Games/SNK_Fighting_Age,Games/SNK_Heroines_Tag_Team_Frenzy,Games/SNK_vs_Capcom_Card_Fighters_Clash_SNK_And_Capcom_Version,Games/SNK_vs_Capcom_Card_Fighters_DS,Games/The_King_of_Fighters_2000,Games/The_King_of_Fighters_2001,Games/The_King_of_Fighters_2002_Challenge_to_Ultimate_Battle,Games/The_King_of_Fighters_2002_Unlimited_Match,Games/The_King_of_Fighters_2003,Games/The_King_of_Fighters_2006,Games/The_King_of_Fighters_98_Ultimate_Match_Online,Games/The_King_of_Fighters_99,Games/The_King_of_Fighters_AllStar,Games/The_King_of_Fighters_Destiny,Games/The_King_of_Fighters_Encounter,Games/The_King_of_Fighters_Evolution,Games/The_King_of_Fighters_EX_Neo_Blood,Games/The_King_of_Fighters_EX2_Howling_Blood,Games/The_King_of_Fighters_for_Girls,Games/The_King_of_Fighters_i_002,Games/The_King_of_Fighters_Maximum_Impact,Games/The_King_of_Fighters_Maximum_Impact_Regulation_A,Games/The_King_of_Fighters_Maximum_Impact_Regulation_A2,Games/The_King_of_Fighters_Neowave,Games/The_King_of_Fighters_NESTS_Hen,Games/The_King_of_Fighters_XI,Games/The_King_of_Fighters_XIII,Games/The_King_of_Fighters_XIV,Games/The_King_of_Fighters_XV | Locations= | People=People/Yuuki_Matsuda | Objects=Objects/Fist | Image=https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_super/0/8072/305543-k_odd.jpg }}
<div id='imageData' data-json='{"infobox":{"file":"305543-k_odd.jpg","path":"0\/8072\/","mime":"image\/jpeg","sizes":"scale_medium,scale_super,square_mini,square_medium,square_small,screen_medium,square_tiny,scale_small,square_avatar,scale_large,scale_avatar,screen_kubrick","caption":""},"background":[]}' />
==History== K' lost all his memories as a young man when he was abducted by NESTS. They injected K' with DNA from [[Characters/Kyo_Kusanagi|Kyo Kusanagi]], one of the most powerful fighters in the world, in order to give him fire abilities of the Kusanagi clan. However, K' betrays NESTS when he realizes he is being used and tries to extract his revenge on the Nests for erasing his memories and using him for their experiments. K' enters the King of Fighters tournaments in order to track down NESTS members and defeat them. K' also partners with [[Characters/Maxima|Maxima]], who went through the same thing as K' and is also trying to get his revenge.
